Battleship Game Created by Kirtan Patel This is a simple Battleship game where you can test your strategic skills against randomly placed enemy ships.
Instructions: 1. The game consists of a 10x10 grid where you will try to sink all enemy ships. 2. You have a limited number of turns to guess the locations of the ships. 3. Each turn, enter your coordinates to attack and check for hits or misses. 4. The enemy ships are represented as follows: - Carrier (5 spaces) - Battleship (4 spaces) - Cruiser (3 spaces) - Submarine (3 spaces) - Destroyer (2 spaces) 5. The game ends when you sink all enemy ships or run out of turns. 6. Have fun and good luck!
